OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with rain or showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy with the odd rumble
OL,8,Fof thunder. Most showers clear through
OL,9,Fthe night, followed by patchy mist and
OL,10,Ffog developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FPatchy mist and fog quickly
OL,13,Fclearing first thing. Otherwise
OL,14,Flargely dry with sunny spells, but
OL,15,Fturning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,16,Fahead of evening rain setting in.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
