OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FFrequent showers on Tuesday, often
OL,7,Fheavy. Generally drier and brighter on
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday, but still the
OL,9,Fodd spot of rain possible.
